reviewText: Very pleased w/my order, as always!
All the discs skipped will not be ordering from this seller again
My daughter is a HUGE fan of this show - so I bought her the collection for her birthday.  she loved it!!!
Great buy, absolutely love it! Great quality and condition!! Received a lil late but that's better than not receiving at all, like some other orders of mine.
My daughter was thrilled with these. I only wish they had come in some kind of nice box set rather than individual-maybe they don't make them like that?
Love all of the American Horror stories!!!
2 of the disks did not work and if I returned it they were going to charge me 50% to send it back. Stay away from this company.
